@startuml
!pragma layout smetana
title 10. Supervisor Agent Deployment Runtime (Decoupled & Worker-ready)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

node "API Runtime (FastAPI)" #E8F8F5 {
  [main.py / uvicorn] as API
  [supervisor_a2a_endpoint] as Endpoint
  [SupervisorAgentService] as AgentService
  [TaskEventStreamService] as EventService
}

node "Background Worker Runtime" #F9E79F {
  [worker.py / main] as Worker
  [SupervisorGraphExecutionService] as GraphExecution
  [SupervisorProgressPublisher] as Publisher
  [LlmSupervisorResponseComposeService] as Composer
}

database "Redis Infra" #FDF2E9 {
  [package:supervisor:task_queue] as TaskQueue
  [package:supervisor:events] as EventStream
  [package:supervisor:session:*] as SessionStore
  [package:supervisor:idempotency:*] as Idempotency
}

cloud "LLM Providers" as LlmProviders

node "Downstream A2A Agents" as Downstream {
  [Product Agent]
  [Reservation Agent]
}

API --> Endpoint
Endpoint --> AgentService
Endpoint --> EventService : SSE Subscription

AgentService --> Idempotency : check_and_reserve (SET NX)
AgentService --> TaskQueue : LPUSH (Task Submission)

Worker --> TaskQueue : BRPOPLPUSH (Reliable Queue)
Worker --> GraphExecution : execute_plan
GraphExecution --> Publisher : publish events
Publisher --> EventStream : XADD

GraphExecution --> Composer : stream_compose
Composer --> LlmProviders : astream

GraphExecution --> Downstream : A2A JSON-RPC calls

note right of API
Independent Runtime:
- ROOT .venv shared for libs
- PYTHONPATH=. for source isolation
- PORT 8000
end note

note bottom of TaskQueue
All keys prefixed with 'package:'
via RedisNamespace.GLOBAL_PREFIX
end note
@enduml
